author: Warhammer
description:
Next weekend's a big one! The General's Handbook 2025-2026 arrives for Warhammer Age of Sigmar, along with Spearhead: Sand and Bone, and fresh Spearhead boxed sets. 

War horns blare in Warhammer: The Old World as the Beastmen Brayherds burst from the undergrowth alongside some classic Wood Elf Realms and High Elf Realms miniatures coming to Made to Order for a limited time.

Plus, sit back and enjoy the first episode of the action-packed animated series Kill Lupercal, and four cracking end of season specials on Warhammer TV – landing this Wednesday.

Follow for more Warhammer, more often! https://www.warhammer-community.com/en-gb/articles/ck4pqjsu/sunday-preview-change-comes-to-the-mortal-realms-and-the-brayherds-raid-the-old-world/
